==English==
===Conjunction===
'''wherewith''' <br>
{{archaic}}
#out of which; by means of which
#:{{RQ:Authorized Version}} Zechariah 14:12 ''And this shall be the plague '''wherewith''' the LORD will smite all the people that have fought against Jerusalem''
===Adverb===
'''wherewith''' <br>
{{archaic}}
# with which; with what
#:{{RQ:Authorized Version}} Matthew 5:13 ''Ye are the salt of the earth: but if the salt have lost his savour, '''wherewith''' shall it be salted?''